        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName><hi rend="print">Down, | Beckenham, Kent. | Railway Station | Orpington. S.E.R.</hi></placeName>
                    <date>April 8<hi rend="superscript">th</hi></date>
                    <salute>Dear Sir</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>There is not the least occasion to apologise to me. On the contrary I thank you <hi rend="underline">sincerely</hi> for your kindness in being willing to correct an error into which you thought that I had fallen, &amp; into which I might easily have fallen.</p>
<p>With my best respects &amp; thanks | I remain Dear Sir | Yours faithfully | Charles Darwin</p> 
                </div>
            </div>
